les, slow connections, unusual inputs — that paid alternatives often hide behind sign-up walls.\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://freetoolshed.com/about\\\",\\\"worksFor\\\":{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Organization\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Free Tool Shed\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://freetoolshed.com\\\"}}\"}}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-3 text-xs text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":[\"Built and maintained by\",\" \",[\"$\",\"$L4\",null,{\"href\":\"/about\",\"className\":\"font-medium text-foreground underline-offset-4 hover:underline\",\"rel\":\"author\",\"children\":\"James Nicolaus\"}],\"$undefined\"]}]]\n1d:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"aria-label\":\"Summary\",\"className\":\"mt-6 rounded-lg border border-brand/30 bg-brand/5 p-4\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm leading-relaxed text-foreground\",\"children\":\"Free Tool Shed's Interactive Periodic Table covers all 118 elements with temperature-driven phase transitions, property heatmaps, an electron configuration viewer, a molar mass calculator, and CSV/JSON data export. Built for chemistry students and educators. No sign-up — a free alternative to Merck PTE and the Royal Society of Chemistry's interactive table.\"}]}]\n1e:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-6 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Temperature Phase Visualization\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Drag a slider from 0K to 6000K and watch all 118 elements change state in real-time. See which elements are solid, liquid, or gas at any temperature.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Property Heatmaps\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-fo