y. Select electronegativity, atomic radius, ionization energy, or density to see the entire table as a color gradient.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Molar Mass Calculator\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Type any chemical formula and get instant molar mass with a full element-by-element breakdown. Supports complex formulas with parentheses.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Element Comparison & Export\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Compare 2–4 elements side by side with bar charts. Export data as CSV, JSON, or PDF. Every property for all 118 elements, completely free.\"}]]}]]}]\n1f:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-8\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L2a\",null,{}]}]\n20:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"my-8 flex justify-center\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L16\",null,{\"slot\":\"mid-content\"}]}]\n21:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-16 space-y-12\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L2b\",null,{}],[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\",\"children\":\"Free Interactive Periodic Table Online\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-3 max-w-3xl text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Explore every element in the periodic table with an interactive, feature-rich tool that rivals paid apps like Merck PTE and Periodic Table Pro — completely free and without signing up. Free Tool Shed's periodic table runs entirely in your browser with no downloads or accounts required. Search by name, symbol, or atomic number. Visualize property trends with heatmaps. Watch phase transitions in real time with the temperature slider. Calculate molar masses, build electron configurations, compare elements side by side, and export data in four formats.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\",\"children\":\"Features\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 grid max-w-3xl gap-3 sm:grid-cols-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",\"All 118 elements with 20+ properties each\",{\"className\":\"flex items-start gap-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-brand\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"All 118 elements with 20+ properties each\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Color-coded by category — alkali metals, noble gases, transition metals, and more\",{\"className\":\"flex items-start gap-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-brand\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Color-coded by category — alkali metals, noble gases, transition metals, and more\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Temperature mode — slide from 0 K to 6000 K and watch elements change phase\",{\"className\":\"flex items-start gap-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-brand\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Temperature mode — slide from 0 K to 6000 K and watch elements change phase\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Property heatmaps — visualize electronegativity, density, atomic radius, and 5 more\",{\"className\":\"flex items-start gap-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-brand\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Property heatmaps — visualize electronegativity, density, atomic radius, and 5 more\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Molar ma