ly visible at a glance.\"}]]}]\n48:[\"$\",\"div\",\"How do I compare elements?\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"dt\",null,{\"className\":\"font-medium text-foreground\",\"children\":\"How do I compare elements?\"}],[\"$\",\"dd\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Click the Compare button in the toolbar, then click up to 4 elements on the table. A comparison panel appears below with bar charts for atomic mass, electronegativity, atomic radius, ionization energy, density, melting point, boiling point, and electron affinity.\"}]]}]\n26:[[\"$\",\"meta\",\"0\",{\"charSet\":\"utf-8\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"1\",{\"name\":\"viewport\",\"content\":\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"}]]\n49:I[27201,[\"/_next/static/chunks/0zif8_3mgcc0x.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0zv.me6xdrdsz.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0ag6f0zogt0qg.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/04p0ygcx_g620.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0d3shmwh5_nmn.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0_pa1c_tsbiw0.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/10nuyoal1pib2.js\"],\"IconMark\"]\n29:[[\"$\",\"title\",\"0\",{\"children\":\"Free Interactive Periodic Table Online — No Sign Up | Free Tool Shed\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"1\",{\"name\":\"description\",\"content\":\"Explore all 118 elements with interactive visualizations, temperature phase changes, property heatmaps, and a molar mass calculator. A free alternative to Merck PTE. No sign up required.\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"2\",{\"name\":\"google-adsense-account\",\"content\":\"ca-pub-7700405385978151\"}],[\"$\",\"link\",\"3\",{\"rel\":\"canonical\",\"href\":\"https://freetoolshed.com/tools/periodic-table\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"4\",{\"property\":\"og:title\",\"content\":\"Free Interactive Periodic Table Online — No Sign Up | Free Tool Shed\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"5\",{\"property\":\"og:description\",\"content\":\"Explore all 118 elements with interactive visualizations, temperature phase changes, property heatmaps, and a molar mass calculator. A free alternative to Merck 